Adding visual charts- Number of Plants By Plant Age Group Line and Clustered Column Chart 35
Number of Plants By Plant Age Group
Click on an empty space on the canvas, from the Visualization pane Select Line and Clustered Column Chart
Fill the value fields provided below for the necessary fields
Build Visual: 
  • X-Axis = Plant Age Group
  • Column Y-Axis = Num of plants
  • Line Y-Axis = % Maint Needed, % Total Cap Maint, Avg Maint Prob
  • Tooltips =  % Maint Needed, % Total Cap Maint, Avg Maint Prob, Num of plants ,  Decade 

Format Visual:
General:
Height = 299
Width = 370
Horizontal = 621
Vertical = 80
Title -> On
Text = Number of Plants By Age Group
Font = Segoe UI, Size = 12
Text color = # FFFFFF
Background color = # a38600
Horizontal Alignment = Center
Background -> On
Color = #F8F6EB
Transparency = 0%
Header Icons -> on
Color-> Background = #FFFFFF, Border = #FFFFFF, Icon = #333333
Transparency = 0%
Tooltip -> On
Text: Font = Segoe UI, Size = 11, Label Color = #252423, Value color = #252423
Background -> Color = #FFFFFF, Transparency = 0%

Visual:
X-Axis =>Values=on: Font = Segoe UI, Size = 12, Color =#000000, Title = off
Y-Axis ->value= On, Font = Segoe UI, Size = 12, Color =#000000, Title = off
Secondary Y-Axis => On, Values: Font = Segoe UI, Size = 12, Color =#000000, Title = off
Legend -> On, Position - Top Left, Style = Marker(Circle default), Text Font =Segoe UI, Size = 9 , Color = #000000, Title = off
Line=> Num of plant=#a38600 ,  % Maint= a666b0, %Total cap maint=#094780, avg maint prob=#f5c4af
Column -> Num of plants=#a38600
